Verse 1
Yadange wanjye, iyo ndebye amaso yawe,
numva isi ihindutse paradizo.
Intambwe zawe zinyereka inzira,
urukundo rwawe rumbwira ngo ntatinya.

Iyo uje hafi yanjye, umutima uranyeganyega,
Ijwi ryawe rikamfasha guhumeka.
Wanyigishije ko gukunda bishoboka,
ko umutima ushobora kongera kwizera.

Pre-Chorus
Uri impano nahawe nâ€™ijuru,
uri isengesho ryasubijwe.

Chorus
Yadange, ndagukunda birenze amagambo,
uri inzozi zabaye impamo.
Yadange, uri impamvu yo guseka kwanjye,
ndagusaba ntuzigere unyibagiza.

Verse 2
Nâ€™iyo imvura iguye ku byishimo byanjye,
izina ryawe riranyongerera imbaraga.
Mu maboko yawe mbona urugo,
mu mutima wawe mbona amahoro.

Iyo wanyegereye, ibikomere birakira,
urukundo rwawe rukansubiza ubuzima.
Sinzi ejo rizaba rimeze gute,
ariko nzi ko nzaribana nawe.

Pre-Chorus
Uri indirimbo umutima wanjye uririmba,
buri munsi.

Chorus
Yadange, ndagukunda birenze amagambo,
uri inzozi zabaye impamo.
Yadange, uri urumuri rwâ€™ubuzima bwanjye,
ntuzigere unyibagiza.

Bridge
Ndagusezeranya umutima wanjye,
si amafaranga, si icyubahiro,
ni wowe nahisemo,
kandi nzaguhitamo buri munsi.

Final Chorus
Yadange, mpaka izuba rizarenga,
ndagukunda kugeza inyenyeri zizaruhuka.
Ndi Appolinaire, umutima wanjye ni uwawe,
